  (text_box "Description: Source OR-ing. Schottky diode-OR (D3/D4, ~0.3 V) combining USBC_VOUT and TPS54360_VOUT into BQ24075_VIN - whichever source is higher feeds the charger; the lower one's diode reverse-biases."
    (at 226.06 83.82 0) (size 48.26 15.24)
    (stroke (width 0) (type default))
    (fill (type color) (color 255 255 194 1))
    (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27) bold) (justify left top))
    (uuid 2c368258-0844-4d6a-94bf-64686ea748a5)
  )
  (text_box "Description: Li-Ion Charger & Power Path (BQ24075). Charger (U2) fed from BQ24075_VIN; powers the system at OUT (BQ24075_OUT) while charging the cell at BAT (DEV_BATT+). Configuration via SYSOFF/CE/EN1/EN2, charge/input current set by R5/R4 (ISET/ILIM), safety timer R3 (TMR), IN cap C1, BAT/OUT bulk caps C2/C4, and status LEDs D1/D2 (R6/R7). TS (BQ24075_TS) is the battery-temperature input."
    (at 279.4 25.4 0) (size 114.3 10.16)
    (stroke (width 0) (type default))
    (fill (type color) (color 255 255 194 1))
    (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27) bold) (justify left top))
    (uuid 507206f7-ef17-4381-b5c2-f1a3262c13ca)
  )
  (text_box "Description: Vehicle Input Protection. Front end for the 12 V automotive line: fuse F1 (2 A), reverse-polarity P-FET Q1 (gate pull-down R15, gate-source Zener clamp D6 15 V), transient suppressor D7 (TVS), and bulk cap C12, producing the protected TPS54360_VIN."
    (at 139.7 83.82 0) (size 81.28 10.16)
    (stroke (width 0) (type default))
    (fill (type color) (color 255 255 194 1))
    (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27) bold) (justify left top))
    (uuid 5dec4369-0d76-4824-a196-5ecd7688ee37)
  )
  (text_box "Description: Fuel Gauge (MAX17048). I²C battery monitor (U3) measuring cell state-of-charge. CELL/VDD tie to DEV_BATT+ with bypass C3 (0.1 µF); SDA/SCL/ALRT (MAX17048_*) report to the MCU; CTG/QSTRT/GND/EP per datasheet.\n"
    (at 279.4 83.82 0) (size 114.3 10.16)
    (stroke (width 0) (type default))
    (fill (type color) (color 255 255 194 1))
    (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27) bold) (justify left top))
    (uuid 9fae7943-b47b-41da-9458-b3f6ae6ede59)
  )
  (text_box "Description:\n\nUSB-C receptacle (J1) providing the 5 V bench/charging port.\nCC1/CC2 pulled down by R1/R2 (5.1 kΩ) to advertise a sink/UFP role;\nD+/D− pass through the ESD/TVS array (U1) to USBC_D±;\nVBUS is brought out as USBC_VOUT to the source-OR."
    (at 22.86 30.48 0) (size 35.56 25.4)
    (stroke (width 0) (type default))
    (fill (type color) (color 255 255 194 1))
    (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27) (thickness 0.254) bold) (justify left top))
    (uuid e626fe67-adc5-4063-b76d-d4df3ce6e5f2)
  )
  (text_box "Description: Battery / Power Connectors. Screw/JST terminals: J2 = EXT_BATT+ (the 12 V vehicle feed) and J3 = DEV_BATT+ (the lithium cell). Two distinct power sources, clearly separated.\n"
    (at 22.86 83.82 0) (size 111.76 7.62)
    (stroke (width 0) (type default))
    (fill (type color) (color 255 255 194 1))
    (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27) bold) (justify left top))
    (uuid e9dc5a21-9001-4f36-acce-6951513b6383)
  )
  (text_box "Description: 12 V Buck (TPS54360 → ~5.2 V). Wide-input automotive step-down (U4) converting the protected vehicle rail TPS54360_VIN down to TPS54360_VOUT (~5.2 V with the present R13/R14 divider). Includes input caps C5/C6, EN/UVLO divider R10/R11, frequency-set R9 on RT/CLK, BOOT cap C7, inductor L1 with catch diode D5, output caps C8/C9, and the COMP network R12/C10/C11."
    (at 139.7 25.4 0) (size 134.62 10.16)
    (stroke (width 0) (type default))
    (fill (type color) (color 255 255 194 1))
    (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27) bold) (justify left top))
    (uuid f621aa21-1081-4dfe-b358-dcc050290d64)
  )

